tachyon.client.keyvalue

Class BaseKeyValueStores

  • java.lang.Object
    • tachyon.client.keyvalue.BaseKeyValueStores
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    KeyValueStores

    @PublicApi
public class BaseKeyValueStores
extends Object
implements KeyValueStores
    Default implementation of the KeyValueStores interface. Developers can extend this class instead of implementing the interface. This implementation reads and writes key-value data through BaseKeyValueStoreReader and BaseKeyValueStoreWriter.
